  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"XuZS7s0N\">      虽然新的《婚姻法》没有了强制婚前检查的规定，但是对于新婚的二人来讲，还是比较建议进行婚前检查。婚检还不仅仅是一项健康检查，更重要的是向人们传播有关婚育健康的知识，进行健康婚育指导。比如，医疗保健机构会向准新人播放婚前医疗卫生知识、婚后计划生育等方面的宣传片，发放宣传材料，开展有关咨询和指导等。</p><p data-pid=\"-YgjPiu-\"><b>必查项目：</b></p><p data-pid=\"YU_ZIC68\">1．<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=401680667&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%9A%E4%BC%A0%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">法定传染病<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>。包括艾滋病、淋病、梅毒、乙肝等，这些疾病可以通过抽血或涂片排查。</p><p data-pid=\"oUmWhCiT\">2．较重的精神病。如严重的<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=401680667&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%BA%81%E7%8B%82%E7%97%87&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">躁狂症<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baike.baidu.com/item/%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25A3%2582%25E7%2597%2587/33032\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">精神分裂症</a>等，这些疾病可能危害他人生命安全和身体健康，患者的心理问题还会引起很多严重后果。此类疾病需要精神科医生诊断。</p><p data-pid=\"afFUt-eB\">3．<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=401680667&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%94%9F%E6%AE%96%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%95%B8%E5%BD%A2&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">生殖系统畸形<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>。此类疾病直接影响生育，其中一些疾病男科和妇科医生可通过肉眼诊断，有些需要用B超检查。</p><p data-pid=\"XV-tJXyV\">4．先天性遗传疾病。如白化病、<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=401680667&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%8E%9F%E5%8F%91%E6%80%A7%E7%99%AB%E7%97%AB&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">原发性癫痫<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>、软骨发育不良、强直性肌营养不良、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baike.baidu.com/item/%25E9%2581%2597%25E4%25BC%25A0%25E6%2580%25A7%25E8%25A7%2586%25E7%25BD%2591%25E8%2586%259C%25E8%2589%25B2%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E5%258F%2598%25E6%2580%25A7/15532851\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">遗传性视网膜色素变性</a>等。遗传性疾病的排查需要检测染色体。</p><p data-pid=\"qoVElHbo\">5．血常规及尿常规。</p><p data-pid=\"K8lT9oDV\"><b>自选项目：</b></p><p data-pid=\"fBBONhZ_\">1．肺功能。一般拍<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=401680667&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=X%E5%85%89%E8%83%B8%E7%89%87&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">X光胸片<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>即可。</p><p data-pid=\"0jyMgznR\">2．心功能。一般的心脏病做心电图即可筛查，先天性心脏病可做<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baike.baidu.com/item/%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2584%258F%25E5%25BD%25A9%25E8%25B6%2585\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">心脏彩超</a>。</p><p data-pid=\"S01IZyXd\">3．血糖。验血查是否有<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baike.baidu.com/item/%25E7%25B3%2596%25E5%25B0%25BF%25E7%2597%2585\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">糖尿病</a>。</p><p data-pid=\"Ht5Lr1Xa\">4．血压。验血查血压是否过高或过低。</p><p data-pid=\"jxnI43JK\">5．内脏。做B超可查肝、胆、胰、脾、肾是否异常。</p><p data-pid=\"CnRsLsOf\">6．血液。抽血查<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baike.baidu.com/item/%25E8%2582%259D%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2583%25BD\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">肝功能</a>、肾功能是否正常。</p><p data-pid=\"l95zd52Y\">       除了上述相关的婚前检查以外，还有一个问题需要关注的是：婚前检查是对男女双方身体健康状况的常规检查，不能检测出<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baike.baidu.com/item/%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AD%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2582%25B2%25E7%2597%2587/2397505\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">不孕不育症</a>。如需该类检查，可以到医院的生殖中心做个全面的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baike.baidu.com/item/%25E5%25AD%2595%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%25A3%2580%25E6%259F%25A5\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">孕前检查</a>。像是女性输卵管检查，排卵情况，免疫因素，激素水平，<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=401680667&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%97%85%E5%8E%9F%E5%BE%AE%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">病原微生物感染<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>等，男方的精子精液质量，内生殖器发育，免疫抗体等都是需要进一步检查的。</p><p data-pid=\"V_p6F3MW\">       经常在临床中能碰到这种情况，刚结婚年轻的时候一直避孕不准备生育，后来年龄大了想要备孕的时候发现不能自然怀孕。来生殖中心检查发现，男方可能存在无精症，少精或畸形精子症等，女方可能存在排卵障碍、卵巢功能以及生殖相关部位畸形或功能不全等。可能会随着年龄的增大错过最佳的治疗时机，所以婚前检查还是很有必要的，可以及时的发现相关问题并进行干预。</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
